# Voice extraction API (multipart/form-data: audio, currentState, language)
# Defaults to http://localhost:8080/api/voice/extract when unset.
REACT_APP_VOICE_API_URL=http://localhost:8080/api/voice/extract

# Manual test plan:
# 1. Start backend on :8080 and run npm start
# 2. Open /accident step, tap mic FAB, speak, tap green check
# 3. Verify fields populate from response claimsData
# 4. Navigate forward/back — voice data persists via sessionStorage
# 5. Record again — API-returned fields overwrite existing values
# Note: Microphone requires HTTPS in production (localhost is exempt).
# Note: Backend must allow CORS from the CRA dev origin (http://localhost:3000).
